divs: Sighting Detailsawoke from a bad dream, went outside and saw usual subject now in northern sky, and suddenly 3 separate objects appeared and traveled north to south, separately, not together, 2 of them were headed due south but 3rd one was headed south and turned east. All 3 were visable for 5 minutes minimum then disappeared, due to impending sunrise ? Have seen the same object in sky over a year but now 3 others moving at great rate of speed accross sky, no noise, no lights just reflecting off sun beyond horizon. this was 1st time ever saw anything like this before
Summary: 3 objects traveling north to south, tracked each for 5 mins then disappeared.
